        <scopecontent id="ref1">
            <head>Scope and Contents note</head>
            <p>Five typescripts of the story board accompanying a 35mm slide presentation, "Saga of the Afro-American Soldiers in the Abraham Lincoln Brigade." Each typescript has different handwritten edits. Accompanying the scripts is a list of African-American volunteers. The slide show covers African-American history from Crispus Attucks to the Spanish Civil War. Includes two trays of 35mm slides.</p>
